      "difficulty": "Easy",
      "solution": "The order of stability of free radicals \n<br><br>$${\\left( {{C_6}{H_5}} \\right)_3}\\,\\mathop C\\limits^ \\bullet   &gt; {\\left( {{C_6}{H_5}} \\right)_2}\\mathop C\\limits^ \\bullet  H &gt; {\\left( {C{H_3}} \\right)_3}\\mathop C\\limits^ \\bullet   &gt; {\\left( {C{H_3}} \\right)_2}\\mathop C\\limits^ \\bullet  H$$ \n<br><br>The stabilisation of first two is due to resonance and last two is due to inductive effect. ",
