      "questionText": "<p>Given below are four compounds :</p><p>(a) n-propyl chloride &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(b) iso-propyl chloride</p><p>(c) sec-butyl chloride &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(d) neo-pentyl chloride</p><p>Percentage of carbon in the one which exhibits optical isomerism is :</p>",
