      "questionText": "The increasing order of reactivity of the\nfollowing compounds towards aromatic\nelectrophilic substitution reaction is :\n<img src=\"https://imagex.cdn.examgoal.net/18hoxe66ijwhwlkvy/bc201ab9-e499-4f3d-893d-4d80b3653e49/c61a01e0-86d5-11e9-8081-1d558b7f1d26/file-18hoxe66ijwhwlkvz.png\" style=\"max-width: 100%;  height: auto;display: block;margin: 0 auto;\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"JEE Main 2019 (Online) 9th April Morning Slot Chemistry - Basics of Organic Chemistry Question 227 English\">",
